---
layout: base.njk
title: Oikos – Bouwend Bureau | Den Haag
description: Duurzame renovatie met hennepvezels. Guido Bouwman maakt woningen klaar voor 2050.
---

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section id="home" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-end pb-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src="/assets/img/oikos-10.jpg" alt="Oikos project" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
    <div class="hero-overlay absolute inset-0"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 w-full">
    <p class="text-oikos-green font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-xs mb-6">
      Oikos – Bouwend Bureau &nbsp;·&nbsp; Den Haag
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-white text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-none mb-8 max-w-3xl">
      Gebouwd met<br>wat de aarde<br>geeft.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-white/70 text-xl max-w-lg mb-14 font-light leading-relaxed">
      Renovatie met hennepvezels en luchtdichte detaillering. Voor gebouwen met karakter — en ambities voor de lange termijn.
    </p>

    <!-- Stats bar -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-white/10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden max-w-3xl">
      <div class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur px-6 py-5">
        <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">90%</p>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-xs mt-1 uppercase tracking-widest">Energiebesparing mogelijk</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur px-6 py-5">
        <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-oikos-green">CO₂−</p>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-xs mt-1 uppercase tracking-widest">Negatief materiaal</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur px-6 py-5">
        <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">0%</p>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-xs mt-1 uppercase tracking-widest">Formaldehyde</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-black/30 backdrop-blur px-6 py-5">
        <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">16u</p>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-xs mt-1 uppercase tracking-widest">Thermische faseverschuiving</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== PROJECTEN & BLOGS – CENTRAAL ===== -->
<section id="projecten" class="py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

    <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-16">
      <div>
        <span class="section-tag">Projecten & kennis</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark leading-tight">
          Wat we maken,<br>schrijven we op.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/nieuws/" class="text-oikos-green hover:text-oikos-green-dark font-semibold text-sm flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors">
        Alle berichten
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    {%- set allPosts = collections.post | reverse -%}

    {% if allPosts.length > 0 %}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <!-- Featured post – groot -->
      {%- set featured = allPosts[0] -%}
      <article class="lg:col-span-2 card-hover group">
        <a href="{{ featured.url }}" class="block">
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-[16/9] bg-oikos-green-light mb-5">
            {% if featured.data.image %}
            <img src="{{ featured.data.image }}" alt="{{ featured.data.title }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" />
            {% else %}
            <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <img src="/assets/logo-hart.png" alt="Oikos" class="h-16 opacity-20" />
            </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="bg-oikos-green-light text-oikos-green text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">{{ featured.data.category or "Nieuws" }}</span>
            <span class="text-oikos-gray text-xs">{{ featured.date | dutchDate }}</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-oikos-dark group-hover:text-oikos-green transition-colors leading-snug mb-3">{{ featured.data.title }}</h3>
          <p class="text-oikos-gray leading-relaxed">{{ featured.data.excerpt }}</p>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- Kleinere posts -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        {% for post in allPosts %}
          {% if loop.index > 1 and loop.index <= 3 %}
          <article class="card-hover group flex-1">
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="block">
              <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl aspect-video bg-oikos-green-light mb-4">
                {% if post.data.image %}
                <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" />
                {% else %}
                <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
                  <img src="/assets/logo-hart.png" alt="Oikos" class="h-10 opacity-20" />
                </div>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <span class="bg-oikos-green-light text-oikos-green text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">{{ post.data.category or "Nieuws" }}</span>
                <span class="text-oikos-gray text-xs">{{ post.date | dutchDate }}</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-oikos-dark group-hover:text-oikos-green transition-colors leading-snug">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
            </a>
          </article>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

    </div>
    {% else %}
    <p class="text-oikos-gray text-center py-16">
      Er zijn nog geen berichten. Voeg ze toe via <a href="/admin/" class="text-oikos-green underline">het admin-panel</a>.
    </p>
    {% endif %}

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== MATERIAAL – HENNEPVEZELS ===== -->
<section id="materiaal" class="py-28 bg-oikos-dark overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

    <div class="mb-16">
      <span class="text-oikos-green text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3 block">Het materiaal</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight max-w-xl">
        Hennep groeit.<br>Isoleert. Ademt.<br>En breekt af.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">

      <!-- Links: uitleg + eigenschappen -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Oikos werkt met biobased materialen, samengesteld op basis van bouwfysica — niet op basis van marketing. De kern is <strong class="text-white">EXIE CaNaDry</strong>, een droge kalkhennep van Belgische bodem.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Samen met luchtdichte detaillering leidt dit tot een energiebesparing van tot 90% op de energierekening. Alles zonder formaldehyde of andere giftige stoffen.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-oikos-green/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-oikos-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">16 uur thermische faseverschuiving</p>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">CaNaDry bij 24 cm dikte vertraagt warmtedoorvoer met 16 uur — koel in de zomer, warm in de winter.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-oikos-green/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-oikos-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Dampdoorlatend — geen vochtstapeling</p>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">Kalkhennep regelt vocht actief, wat schimmelvorming in oude constructies tegengaat — zonder dampscherm nodig.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-oikos-green/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-oikos-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">CO₂-negatief over de hele levenscyclus</p>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">Hennep bindt CO₂ tijdens de groei. Kalk herneemt CO₂ bij verharding. Het materiaal is per saldo koolstofnegatief.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-oikos-green/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-oikos-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Zonder formaldehyde of giftige stoffen</p>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">Alle gebruikte materialen zijn getest en vrij van schadelijke emissies — voor een gezonde woning van binnenuit.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Rechts: Materiaalkaart + foto's -->
      <div class="space-y-6">

        <!-- Materiaalkaart – uniek element -->
        <div class="border border-white/10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-oikos-green/10 border-b border-white/10 px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div>
              <p class="text-oikos-green text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase">Materiaalkaart</p>
              <p class="text-white font-bold mt-0.5">EXIE CaNaDry — droge kalkhennep</p>
            </div>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-oikos-green opacity-60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="divide-y divide-white/5">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 px-6 py-3">
              <span class="text-white/40 text-sm">λ-waarde</span>
              <span class="text-white font-mono text-sm">0,054 W/m·K</span>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 px-6 py-3">
              <span class="text-white/40 text-sm">Faseverschuiving</span>
              <span class="text-white font-mono text-sm">16 uur (24 cm)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 px-6 py-3">
              <span class="text-white/40 text-sm">CO₂-balans</span>
              <span class="text-oikos-green font-mono text-sm font-bold">Negatief</span>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 px-6 py-3">
              <span class="text-white/40 text-sm">Dichtheid</span>
              <span class="text-white font-mono text-sm">175 kg/m³</span>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 px-6 py-3">
              <span class="text-white/40 text-sm">Formaldehyde</span>
              <span class="text-oikos-green font-mono text-sm font-bold">Geen</span>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 px-6 py-3">
              <span class="text-white/40 text-sm">Herkomst</span>
              <span class="text-white font-mono text-sm">België</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Foto's -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden aspect-square">
            <img src="/assets/img/oikos-2.jpg" alt="Hennep isolatie" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden aspect-square">
            <img src="/assets/img/oikos-5.jpg" alt="Oikos project" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== OVER OIKOS ===== -->
<section id="over-ons" class="py-28 bg-oikos-green-light">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <div>
        <span class="section-tag">Wie we zijn</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark mb-6 leading-tight">
          Elk pand verdient<br>een eerlijke aanpak.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Oikos is opgericht door Guido Bouwman. Hij werkt met biobased materialen en luchtdichte detaillering — niet omdat het trendy is, maar omdat het werkt. Elk pand is anders, en dat vraagt om een aanpak op maat.
        </p>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Kleine teams, korte lijnen, en materialen die hij zelf door en door kent.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <img src="/assets/logo-hart.png" alt="Oikos" class="h-12 opacity-70" />
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-oikos-dark">Guido Bouwman</p>
            <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm">Oprichter · Oikos Bouwend Bureau · Den Haag</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <img src="/assets/img/guido.png" alt="Guido Bouwman aan het werk" class="w-full object-cover aspect-[4/3]" />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== WERKWIJZE ===== -->
<section id="diensten" class="py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <span class="section-tag">Hoe we werken</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark">Van eerste gesprek<br>tot opgeleverd werk.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 relative">
      <!-- Verbindingslijn -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-8 left-[12.5%] right-[12.5%] h-px bg-oikos-green-light z-0"></div>

      {% set stappen = [
        { nr: "01", titel: "Intake & analyse", tekst: "We kijken naar de constructie, het gebruik en de ambities. Geen standaard offerte — maar een reëel advies op maat." },
        { nr: "02", titel: "Materiaalplan", tekst: "Op basis van de analyse stellen we een plan op. Welke dikte, welke detaillering, hoe aansluitend op bestaand werk." },
        { nr: "03", titel: "Uitvoering", tekst: "Kleine teams, nauwkeurig werk. Heldere communicatie over voortgang en eventuele afwijkingen van het plan." },
        { nr: "04", titel: "Oplevering & meting", tekst: "Na oplevering meten we het resultaat. Blower door test voor luchtdichtheid, thermische inspectie op verzoek." }
      ] %}

      {% for stap in stappen %}
      <div class="text-center relative z-10">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-oikos-green-light border-4 border-white shadow-md flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <span class="text-oikos-green font-extrabold text-sm">{{ stap.nr }}</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-oikos-dark mb-3">{{ stap.titel }}</h3>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">{{ stap.tekst }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== CONTACT ===== -->
<section id="contact" class="py-28 bg-oikos-dark">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <div>
        <span class="text-oikos-green text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4 block">Contact</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Een vraag of<br>een gebouw in gedachten?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Vertel ons over het gebouw, de situatie en de ambitie. Dan kijken we samen wat er mogelijk is.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:info@bureau-oikos.nl" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-oikos-green hover:bg-oikos-green-dark text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors text-base">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          info@bureau-oikos.nl
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-oikos-green mb-2">90%</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">energiebesparing mogelijk met de juiste aanpak</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">CO₂−</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">negatief materiaal over de volledige levenscyclus</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">16u</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">thermische faseverschuiving — koel in de zomer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-oikos-green mb-2">0%</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">formaldehyde in alle gebruikte materialen</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
